reviewText: My niece loved this show as a kid and Keke Palmer is really cute in it!
Very Good Show. Loved it on Nick. I bought the entire series. Very happy with the purchase. They basically ended the show to give more time for Victorious.

I'm very happy with the DVD. It works well and it is like I expected it to be. I used to follow True Jackson VP when I worked in the states, but when I went back to my country I couldn't anymore because the show wasn't aired there. Now I'm very happy to finally get a chance to see season 2 of this series.
